  "title": "Stage compere",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Opening and closing the event</strong>: Introduce the event, welcome the audience, and set the tone.</li>\n  <li><strong>Introducing speakers/performers</strong>: Provide brief, engaging introductions for each act or speaker.</li>\n  <li><strong>Keeping the program on track</strong>: Manage timing, ensuring the event runs according to the schedule.</li>\n  <li><strong>Engaging the audience</strong>: Maintain audience energy and attention, especially between segments.</li>\n  <li><strong>Handling transitions</strong>: Smoothly move from one part of the program to another.</li>\n  <li><strong>Managing unexpected situations</strong>: Improvise in case of delays, technical issues, or other unforeseen events.</li>\n</ul>",
